title: Steve Miller Band - Giants Stadium NJ 1978 FLACak
description:
Steve Miller Band - Giants Stadium NJ  1978 FLACak



First Concert At Giants Stadium

A CROWD of 61,128 people heard the Steve Miller Band at Giants Stadium, In New Jersey's Meadowlands Sports Complex, Sunday afternoon. It was the first rock concert at the stadium, but it probably will not be the last. The crowd was well behaved,(LOL) the facility was run as smoothly and efficiently as one could expect, and the weather was perfect.
Released in 1978, The Steve Miller Band's Greatest Hits 1974–78 has sold over 13 million copies, and Miller continues to perform sold-out concerts
